*
!README.md
!AGENTS.md
!docs/
!docs/**
!json_prompt/
!json_prompt/**
!log/
!log/**
!Veritas/
!Veritas/**
!.gitignore

# ============================================================
# 敏感文件 — 即使在白名单目录中也必须忽略
# 规则：Git 中后匹配的规则优先级更高，以下规则覆盖上方的 ! 白名单
# ============================================================

# --- 环境变量（含密钥/密码/API Key）---
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.env.production
**/.env.staging

# --- Spring Boot 敏感配置 ---
**/application-dev.yml
**/application-prod.yml
**/application-dev.properties
**/application-prod.properties

# --- 密钥与证书 ---
**/*.key
**/*.pem
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
**/*.jks
**/*.keystore
**/*.truststore
**/secrets/
**/certs/

# --- 数据库备份与转储 ---
**/*.sql.dump
**/*.sql.gz
**/*.sql.backup
**/db-backup/

# --- 日志文件（可能含敏感运行时信息）---
**/*.log
**/logs/

# --- 操作系统生成文件 ---
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini

# --- 编辑器/IDE 临时文件（可能含本地配置）---
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*~
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/*.iml

# ============================================================
# 编译产物与构建输出 — 无需版本控制
# ============================================================

# --- Java / Maven / Gradle ---
**/target/
**/build/
**/*.class
**/*.jar
**/*.war
**/*.ear
**/.gradle/
**/gradle-app.setting
**/out/

# --- Node.js / 前端 ---
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.vite/
**/.next/
**/.nuxt/
**/.output/

# --- Python ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/*.egg-info/
**/.eggs/
**/build/lib/
**/build/scripts-*/

# --- 通用编译产物 ---
**/*.o
**/*.obj
**/*.so
**/*.dll
**/*.exe
**/*.out
**/*.a
**/*.lib

# ============================================================
# 缓存文件 — 自动生成，无需跟踪
# ============================================================

# --- 前端缓存 ---
**/.cache/
**/.parcel-cache/
**/.turbo/

# --- Python缓存 ---
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov/
**/.tox/
**/.nox/

# --- 操作系统缓存 ---
**/.Trash/
**/Trash/

# ============================================================
# 非核心代码文件 — 开发辅助，非项目核心
# ============================================================

# --- 本地开发配置 ---
**/.envrc
**/local.properties
**/application-local.yml
**/application-local.properties

# --- 测试报告与覆盖率 ---
**/test-results/
**/coverage/
**/*.lcov

# --- 临时文件 ---
**/tmp/
**/temp/
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak
**/*.orig

# --- 依赖锁定文件（可选忽略，视团队约定）---
# **/package-lock.json
# **/yarn.lock
# **/pnpm-lock.yaml
# **/poetry.lock

# --- 文档生成 ---
**/site/
**/apidoc/

# --- 数据库文件 ---
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3
**/*.db

# --- Python 虚拟环境 ---
**/.venv/
**/.venv*/
**/venv/
**/env/
**/.env/
**/virtualenv/
